body.description: Meals can be messy. With Nuby's Baby High Chair Cover, you can keep mealtime simple and clean up easy. The water-resistant high chair cushion cover was designed to protect your toddler high chair from sticky liquids, crumbs, and other stubborn baby food. The baby eating chair cover features elastic backing and side ties for a secure fit, while foam padding softens baby's snack and meal time. Like peas and carrots, with comfort should come safety. The cover fits most full-size baby feeding chairs and portable highchairs with 3- or 5-point harnesses. No matter what, your toddler is safe and snug during mealtime. The High Chair Cover wipes clean for smaller messes, making cleaning a cinch. For those formidable spills, the baby seat cover is machine washable. Regardless of the size or scope of the mess, Nuby's High Chair Cover is made to keep life stress-free.

productInformation.name: Care instructions
productInformation.value: ‎Wash before first use. Machine wash cold on gentle cycle with like colors. Use only non-chlorine bleach when needed. Tumble dry low heat. Do not iron.

reviews.reviewText: Love this! Our high chair is a bit older and needed a replacement cushion. It fits super well over the wooden base and love the easy clean fabric. We even have the old cushion on underneath and it fits well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fit perfectly and washed up really well
reviews.reviewText: Got this to replace my granddaughters high chair cover . It fit perfectly and love that the straps were included also. Looked nice on . She recently had her first birthday and received a smash cake that had red icing on edges. As you can guess the cover got stained. I pretty much figured I'd have to order another but daughter washed it the next day and the stain came out, cover looks brand new still and padding stayed in place! Couldn't be happier with this purchase.

reviews.reviewText: This item is a great price and shipped very quickly. Gave 4 stars because I wish it was padded just a little more, but overall is great quality and for my high chair very well! Easy to clean!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits Graco Table2Table!
reviews.reviewText: I got a Graco Table2Table high chair as a re-sale event. It was in great condition except for the cushion. I thought it would be easy to order a replacement but quickly found out it wasn't. Graco didn't sell replacement cushions. Options on Etsy were insanely expensive (defeating the point of buying a second-hand high chair) and a lot of other options I was finding were really cheap. This was the best one I could find, but I couldn't find anything definitive that said whether this would fit the Graco or not. But it fits perfectly! The material is actually better in my opinion than the original because it looks easy to wipe down. Baby isn't here yet so I don't know about durability but I am happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: The perfect replacment high chair cover.
reviews.reviewText: I'm always a bit hesitant when products are described as a universal fit, but this one did the trick. The material itself is soft enough for my baby to sit in, however, it is lacking a little in padding - but I guess it depends on how picky you are. The material is easy to clean with a wet cloth, the fit is snug on my Greco high chair, the elastic and the ties on the back keep it in place. I'm quite satisfied and recommend it.

I had a PerPerego Tatamia. The original chair replace cover is too expensive to purchase, other generic versions are made with cotton which always requires cleaning.This cover fits perfectly on the chair and easy to be removed for cleaning. Water proof service is baby and child friendly. Note that it is to be used over the old chair cover as it doesn't cover the whole chair. But it covers the majority of the area.Highly recommends it for the quality and price.
